CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 19, 1954, page 21, reads: "The Goode Pharmacy booth looked like a miniture drug store. Mrs. Sarah Jane Goode and William Goode, owners of two drug stores, were on hand to greet the crowd."
TitMainTitle: Sara Jane McPherson Goode and William W. Goode, standing in Goode Pharmacy booth in Hunt Armory for the 1954 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
